# Design System

Design tokens translated from Figma to ensure uniform styling across BA mockups (`ba/req/`) and Dev components (`dev/src/`).

## Color Palette

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--color-primary` | `#2563EB` | Primary actions, links, active states |
| `--color-primary-hover` | `#1D4ED8` | Primary button hover |
| `--color-secondary` | `#64748B` | Secondary text, icons |
| `--color-background` | `#FFFFFF` | Page background |
| `--color-surface` | `#F8FAFC` | Cards, panels, elevated surfaces |
| `--color-border` | `#E2E8F0` | Dividers, input borders |
| `--color-text-primary` | `#0F172A` | Headings, body text |
| `--color-text-secondary` | `#64748B` | Captions, helper text |
| `--color-success` | `#16A34A` | Success states, confirmations |
| `--color-warning` | `#D97706` | Warnings, caution alerts |
| `--color-error` | `#DC2626` | Errors, destructive actions |

